2026-05-04T00:59:56.1134360Z               "message": "Add clear (×) button to validators page domain input\n\nClicking ×  clears the input and immediately reopens the suggestions\ndropdown (via mousedown + e.preventDefault() to avoid losing focus),\nso the user can start typing a new query without extra clicks.\n\nThe button is shown only when the input has content (has-value class\ntoggled by updateClearBtn, called on every input event and after a\nsuggestion is selected), and sits between the text and the ▾ arrow\nbutton with matching muted/hover styles.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_017FwhhWhVeVAy86df4xWeVQ",
